//? Coding

// Game starts upon clicking the start button

// The Borgs move in group left to right all together, one cell per 0.86 seconds(like the heart beat)
// Once they reach the right edge they all move one row down
// Once they move one row down, they start moving right to left
// Once they reach  the left edge they move one row down 
// They repeat this function until they reach the row of the shooter

// Starship moves on the same row left to right and right to left
// Starship is controlled by the player with the arrow keys
// Upon clicking a certain key (maybe x), the Starship shoots laser 

// Laser travels on the same column it is initiated
// Once the laser hits a Borg, the Borg disappears (upon touching the laser it becomes invisible? Or the class gets removed)
// Every time the laser hits a Borg, the Starship gets 1000 points.

// Game ends in two ways. 
// Starship hits all Borgs and Wins
// Or
// Borgs reach the Starship row and Game Over

// In both cases there is a reset button to restart the same


